The Ambulance;;1990;;R;;Action,Comedy,Horror;;5.9;;Larry Cohen;;Eric Roberts,James Earl Jones,Megan Gallagher,Red Buttons,Janine Turner,Eric Braeden,Richard Bright,James Dixon,Jill Gatsby,Martin Barter,Laurene Landon,Nick Chinlund,Matt Norklun,Rudy Jones,Stan Lee,Max,Deborah Hedwall,Susan Blommaert;;Josh Baker meets a very special woman, Cheryl, in the streets of New York. Suddenly she collapses, and she's picked up by an ambulance. When Josh wants to visit her in the hospital, it appears that she hasn't been admitted in the hospital. Josh follows the roommate of Cheryl, and she disappears after a ride in the same ambulance. It's up to Josh to solve the secret behind this strange vehicle.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099026/